This is a Cargo workspace. All crates live under `crates/`:

| Crate | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `{{ project_name }}` | CLI binary{% if has_core_library %} |
| `{{ project_name }}-core` | Shared library (config, types, logic){% endif %}{% if has_xtask %} |
